{
  "extends": ["development"]
}

/*
A .hintrc file is a configuration file used by webhint, a linting tool that 
helps you improve the quality, accessibility, and performance of your websites.

The extends property with the value "development" means that your .hintrc file 
is inheriting a predefined set of webhint rules and configurations designed for 
a "development" environment. This allows you to quickly set up common best 
practices without having to configure every rule individually.
*/
